---
title: Sequence Diagram - Chatbot Cek Ketersediaan Kamar
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Tamu
    participant UI as Halaman /chatbot
    participant API as /api/chat (streamText)
    participant LLM as Gemini 2.5 Flash
    participant Tool as Tool cekKetersediaan
    participant DB as Supabase

    Tamu->>UI: Tanya "Ada kamar 20-22 Juli?"
    UI->>API: POST messages
    API->>LLM: stream({ messages, tools, systemPrompt })
    LLM->>LLM: Deteksi intent ketersediaan
    LLM->>Tool: cekKetersediaan(checkIn, checkOut, tipeKamar?)
    Tool->>DB: SELECT room_id FROM reservations WHERE status NOT IN (...)<br/>AND check_in < ? AND check_out > ?
    DB-->>Tool: busyRoomIds[]
    Tool->>DB: SELECT id, number, type, base_price, image_url FROM rooms<br/>WHERE id NOT IN busyRoomIds AND status NOT IN (maintenance, out_of_order)
    DB-->>Tool: availableRooms[]
    Tool->>DB: SELECT name, amenities, images FROM custom_room_types WHERE name IN (...)
    DB-->>Tool: typeMetadata[]
    Tool-->>LLM: { status: "available", rooms: [...] }
    LLM->>API: Stream token + tool result
    API-->>UI: SSE: kartu interaktif kamar
    UI-->>Tamu: Galeri foto + tarif + tombol "Book This Room"
